io.github.rowak.nanoleafapi

Class Plugin

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.rowak.nanoleafapi.Plugin

  • public class Plugin
extends java.lang.Object
    A local interface for an Aurora plugin. Setter methods in this class will not have an effect on the Aurora.

    • Constructor Summary
